ClojureList<T> - Class in com.github.rschmitt.collider
A generic persistent immutable List implementation, with three types of methods: Read methods from List, such as get(int) Write methods from List, such as add(T); these will throw UnsupportedOperationException and have been marked as @Deprecated Persistent "modification" methods, such as append(T); these will efficiently create modified copies of the current list
